Package fitnessclub

Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
fitnessclub.Schedule
public class Schedule extends Object
Instance stores a Schedule object that represents an array of FitnessClass objects. Contains methods to add and expand the classes array and to load class information from a txt file.
Author:
Ridwan Sharkar, Ashley Berlinski

      fitnessClass - the fitness class that is being searched for in the schedule.
      Returns:

      Returns:
